newsitem.title: USA: Iowa-S Minn cattle market not well tested - USDA.
newsitem.headline: Iowa-S Minn cattle market not well tested - USDA.

text.p: Slaughter steers and heifers not tested, compared with Friday's close, USDA said. Trade slow. Demand and seller interest light. Offerings current.
Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 no sales. Heifers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 no sales.
On a carcass basis (weight only) compared to Friday's close, slaughter steers and heifers not well tested.

Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1300 lbs pt ld 114.00 Holstein - (weight only) Select to mostly Choice 2-3 1250-1400 lbs 2 lds 105.00 Holsteins - ( grade and weight) Choice 2-3 1250-1450 lbs no sales Select 2-3 1250-1450 lbs no sales.
Heifers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 no sales.
